    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bombo Rumble is a 4 player local - multiplayer game where you throw bombs with physics at your foes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore randomized dungeons in single player or Co-op</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319310/extras/07eb9e1114b045f62b63600db87e69fe.avif?t=1750839261\" width=1920 height=1080 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Battle your friends with a variety of ranged weapons to attack them from afar.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319310/extras/48b415508f9d0950b046a725ab2b8108.avif?t=1750839261\" width=743 height=139 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse Bombs and power ups bring mayhem to the fight!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319310/extras/51ad8509804124545f398e58da34d360.avif?t=1750839261\" width=656 height=116 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Battle it out in 12 different Arenas!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319310/extras/80b248a05298957f98f1e6fd7b19bf44.avif?t=1750839261\" width=512 height=382 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If you don't have any friends, don't worry. Play against AI opponents!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319310/extras/7578a5c12ee718c873806dbc3a30cc60.avif?t=1750839261\" width=672 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play online with Remote Play Together </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bombs away! Blast your friends! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Note: Controllers are required for local multiplayer</i></p>",
